# Azenquoria Feature Requirements

## 1. Journal Feature (生活的色彩)
- Allow users to write and save journal entries
- Provide color theme selection for entries
- Generate journal entry cards with selected colors
- Display recent journal entries in a grid view
- Save entries locally using shared_preferences

## 2. Share Feature (生活分享)
- Allow users to create short text snippets for sharing
- Generate visually appealing share cards with the text
- Create QR codes for each shared card
- Provide options to save QR codes to photo gallery
- Allow sharing of generated cards
- Display recent shares in a grid view

## 3. Breathing Exercise Feature (呼吸情绪调节)
- Implement 5 breathing exercise modes:
  - Anxiety Relief (4-7-8 breathing)
  - Focus (box breathing)
  - Quick Relaxation (5-5-5 breathing)
  - Energy Boost (quick alternating breathing)
  - Deep Sleep (slow deep breathing)
- Visual progress indicators with different colors for each mode
- Text instructions guiding users through each breathing phase
- Round tracking and session completion summary
- Ability to pause/stop exercises

## 4. Settings Feature (设置)
- Display user profile information
- Provide the following menu items with colorful icons:
  - Help us improve (帮助我们改进)
  - Quick start guide (快速上手)
  - Beginner's guide (新手指南)
  - Privacy & security (你的隐私与安全)
  - Terms of service (服务条款)
- Each menu item should link to relevant information
- Display as cards with appropriate icons
 